{"tid":1550661,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"知唔知點解依家藍絲廢老頻頻出現","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T18:38:39.000Z","uid":97523,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62e4e7e1a538cf69e777a3550baa82ef2e20d88b","tid":1550661,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:14.000Z","msg":"因係佢地打完你<br />\n原來冇後果<br />\n首先黑警唔會拉唔會理先<br />\n<br />\n試下每次一出現呢啲人<br />\n用口屌既 屌返佢 請佢走<br />\n郁手既 直接還拖私了<br />\n<br />\n我想講以上既野係好重要<br />\n第一凝造個氣氛比藍絲廢老唔好再搞搞陣<br />\n你搞手足會有後果<br />\n<br />\n第二我覺得係最重要<br />\n連郁手在先既黑社會 刀手 藍絲 大陸廢老都唔敢私了既 <br />\n點樣下一步救手足 圍黑警 光復香港？<br />\n<br />\n我地面對緊既係中共香港政權<br />\n義士受緊黑警既強權打壓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">依家出得黎既每分每秒都好重要<br />\n諗部署 退路 留意現場情況 <br />\n冇時間再同啲藍絲廢老左膠內心戲<br />\n有人搞事快手KO完就走啦</span>"},{"pid":"d05542296ffd02bf1078e203718e322911623d2e","tid":1550661,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45e561cef694c69948f41223b957057933099173","tid":1550661,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:06:58.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"cba27d9973c979c904d88de6965b44372db291cf","tid":1550661,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:07:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC7M5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=8885fada\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"c0253e3332b718e20e93e559ebee4eb7c58f43d4","tid":1550661,"uid":31354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:11:09.000Z","msg":"支持私了<br />\n<br />\n呢班廢老以為人地唔打佢<br />\n<br />\n最好打關節，等佢臨落棺材個刻都係永遠都行唔到"},{"pid":"afb4af873dd96a0cefca049823e310e0f1daa51f","tid":1550661,"uid":90873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1008e65baa4a54adc7a18aa150223dac6c738e","tid":1550661,"uid":154667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:58:09.000Z","msg":"721 811 831<br />\n有好多五毛推沉晒啲正事po，小心俾人帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f23840504728a0c1270774ec1e327ad0496a50","tid":1550661,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:58:57.000Z","msg":"「做和理非雖然不幸，但並不可怕，因為知道掙扎，畢竟有掙脫的希望；若是從和理非生活中尋出美來，讚嘆、陶醉，就是萬劫不復的左膠了。」"},{"pid":"ebea8ae5feda1906e16edaee516e6a2dcfc51f1b","tid":1550661,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T18:38:39.000Z","msg":"你班傻閪一想打就有人叫停手, 打斷佢手腳你又唔撚夠膽<br />\n比我都罹刀斬柒你班阻住人搵食既弱者<br />\n反正食滑你地唔敢郁手"}]}